                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <placeName>No. 98 Bowery</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>May 31/67</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee>\n                <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dr. Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Could you favor me<lb/> with a list of the different ministers\n                of<lb/> Congregations in the <placeName>United States</placeName>, or of those<lb/>\n                that you are aware of and their address<lb/> or of the name of your magazine\n                agents<lb/> with whom I could open negotiations in<lb/> reference to my Jewish\n                Family Scenes. I<lb/> know of no way of reaching them unless I<lb/> can receive some\n                of them through information<lb/> of newspapers authorities. If you can<lb/> assist\n                me in the same I will be under<lb/> many obligations.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Respy yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M. Samelson</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30p0x71p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
